_aFiles._sDescription: Includes the .bsp file and a README.txt file for a guide to make it work
If your radar isn't working, follow the steps thought in the README.txt file included in this .rar
If your radar doesn't have names/it wanted you to generate a nav-mesh, then download this and README

_aChangeLog.text: The optimization is now way better.
Creates in T Spawn for Ts to snipe Outside / Side Alley / Long.
Shall your radar/nav file not work, now you can download them seperately and put them in your games folder.

_aLatestUpdates._sText: I had always had problems with paking stuff with .bsp files, and so, if you do have a problem with the radar/nav file, then I left the option for people to download the overview image/nav file if they don't work in-game. Hope this helps, have fun!

_sText:
Worked on this map for about 2/3 months now! Hope you guys like it! This map has: radar-overview, custom nav-mesh for better bots and radar names. The map also goes a lot like de_nuke, with the bombsites on top of each other. Have fun!

From now on, this map will receive updates whenever all of the "to do's" are checked. I will add a few "to do's" whenever I am working on an update, so you can make an idea how it's going to be.

This map is still in its beta stage. I thought some feedback would be useful at this moment.
